high_descs: move to the island ahead of the sink
pick up a fork from the island
move to the island to the left of where you are
put the fork in a glass on the island
pick up the glass from the island
move to the counter behind you
put the glass on the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a fork on the counter to the right of the sink.

Pick the fork up from the table.
Move to the left and face the table.
Put the fork in the glass.
Pick the glass up from the table.
Turn around and stand next to the sink.
Put the glass on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a fork in it on the counter.

high_descs: walk through kitchen to face green kitchen island
pick up the fork closest to the front edge to the left of the frying pan on the green kitchen island
walk left to the left edge of green kitchen island
put fork into the champagne glass on the kitchen island
pick up the glass from the kitchen island
turn left to face the stove with the dishwasher on the left
place the glass on the counter above the dishwasher
anns.task_desc: put a glass and fork on a kitchen counter
